No, I said that.

780
01:03:42,908 --> 01:03:45,342
Cross Leo, next time I'll say plenty.

781
01:03:52,585 --> 01:03:55,521
When you're right,you're right.

782
01:03:55,589 --> 01:03:58,889
But you never say,
''I told you so.''

783
01:03:58,960 --> 01:04:01,053
So what am I right about?

784
01:04:02,464 --> 01:04:05,127
Well, I'll tell you.

785
01:04:05,201 --> 01:04:09,036
But first you gotta promise
not to say I told you so.

786
01:04:09,106 --> 01:04:13,236
I never say that,
and I don't like people who do.

787
01:04:15,880 --> 01:04:18,212
Mink was robbing me right along
with the shmatte.

788
01:04:18,282 --> 01:04:20,217
What convinced you of that?

789
01:04:20,285 --> 01:04:22,583
Mink took a powder.
We can't find him.

790
01:04:22,655 --> 01:04:25,090
The Dane, he's making excuses for him.

791
01:04:25,158 --> 01:04:27,592
But personally, I think you was right.

792
01:04:27,661 --> 01:04:30,290
I think that Mink and Bernie was in it together.

793
01:04:30,364 --> 01:04:33,800
