819
01:06:12,252 --> 01:06:17,350
Of course there's always that wild card
when, uh, love is involved.

820
01:06:20,095 --> 01:06:22,529
I know Mink is Eddie Dane's boy.

821
01:06:24,534 --> 01:06:27,094
Still, I--
I don't make it that way.

822
01:06:28,939 --> 01:06:32,306
