- Of course, then, there's no reason-- Shut up!
- Papa, Papa, I got--

826
01:06:42,521 --> 01:06:45,923
You take a page out of this guy's book.

827
01:06:45,992 --> 01:06:50,020
A little less you talk, a little more you think!

828
01:06:52,300 --> 01:06:54,667
Kids. You gotta be firm.

829
01:06:54,736 --> 01:06:59,469
Anyways, there's no reason not to check things out.

830
01:06:59,541 --> 01:07:02,943
If Mink is around, I want you to find him.
He can tell us what's what.

831
01:07:03,012 --> 01:07:06,073
What's the matter?
Somebody hit you?

832
01:07:06,150 --> 01:07:08,983
What's the matter?
Aren't we friends anymore?

833
01:07:09,053 --> 01:07:11,989
If you find him, I wanna talk to him alone.

834
01:07:12,057 --> 01:07:14,685
That's the way you get
the straight dope--man to man.

835
01:07:14,759 --> 01:07:18,457
Just me, Mink... and my friend Roscoe.

836
01:07:18,531 --> 01:07:21,194
You understand what I'm saying?

837
01:07:21,268 --> 01:07:23,702
- It ain't complicated.

838
01:07:34,416 --> 01:07:38,877
You should leave town for a few days.
 Things are gonna heat up around here.

839
01:07:38,955 --> 01:07:41,390
Go to the Palisades.
I'll join you soon as I'm done.

840
01:07:41,459 --> 01:07:44,394
I can't find Bernie.
Did you find him?

841
01:07:45,696 --> 01:07:47,631
Yeah.

842
01:07:47,699 --> 01:07:49,894
Is he leaving?

843
01:07:49,968 --> 01:07:54,338
He, uh-- He left.

844
01:07:54,407 --> 01:07:57,002
- He say where to?
- He didn't say.

845
01:07:57,077 --> 01:07:59,272
- You--
- Thanks.

846
01:08:16,333 --> 01:08:18,802
- That's Bernie's sister, ain't it?
- Beats me.

847
01:08:18,870 --> 01:08:21,270
- What's he seeing her for?
- Beats me. Maybe--

848
01:08:21,339 --> 01:08:25,106
Shut up. Get lost.

849
01:08:25,177 --> 01:08:27,737
