I'll be sure to tell him.

866
01:09:41,735 --> 01:09:45,797
- Where's Leo?
- If I tell you, how do I know you won't kill me?

867
01:09:45,874 --> 01:09:51,040
Because if you told me and I killed you and you
 were lying, I wouldn't get to kill you then.

868
01:09:51,113 --> 01:09:52,921
- Where's Leo?
- He's moving around.

869
01:09:53,483 --> 01:09:56,367
He's getting his mob together
tomorrow at Whiskey Nick's.

870
01:09:56,759 --> 01:09:57,576
You sure?

871
01:09:57,676 --> 01:09:59,989
Check it. It's gold.

872
01:10:00,057 --> 01:10:03,653
You know what,yegg?
I believe you.

873
01:10:25,853 --> 01:10:27,879
Go ahead and run, sweetie.

874
01:10:27,956 --> 01:10:31,448
I'll track down all of you whores.

875
01:11:31,664 --> 01:11:35,431
Hello, Bernie. Come on in.
Make yourself at home.

876
01:11:35,503 --> 01:11:38,495
Hello, Tom.

877
01:11:38,572 --> 01:11:42,339
I thought I'd do that,
 since you didn't seem to be in.

878
01:11:42,411 --> 01:11:46,576
Figured it was a bad idea to wait in the hall,
seeing as I'm supposed to be dead.

879
01:11:49,685 --> 01:11:52,120
How'd you know it was me?

880
01:11:52,189 --> 01:11:54,680
You're the only one I know
 who'd knock and then break in.

881
01:11:54,758 --> 01:11:56,750
Your other friends wouldn't break in?

882
01:11:56,828 --> 01:12:00,025
My other friends want to kill me,
so they wouldn't knock.

883
01:12:00,098 --> 01:12:02,533
What's on your mind. Bernie?

884
01:12:04,937 --> 01:12:07,338
Things.

885
01:12:07,407 --> 01:12:12,869
I guess you must be angry.
I'm supposed to be gone far away.

886
01:12:12,947 --> 01:12:16,042
I guess it seems sort of irresponsible,
my being here.

887
01:12:18,554 --> 01:12:22,047
And I was gonna leave.
Honest, I was.

888
01:12:22,125 --> 01:12:24,059
But then I started thinking...

889
01:12:24,127 --> 01:12:26,995
if I stuck around,
that would not be good for you.

890
01:12:27,064 --> 01:12:29,794
Then I started thinking that--

891
01:12:29,867 --> 01:12:32,302
that might not be bad for me.

892
01:12:35,540 --> 01:12:38,271
You didn't see the play you gave me.

893
01:12:38,344 --> 01:12:40,608
I mean, what am I gonna do?

894
01:12:40,680 --> 01:12:43,616
If I leave, I got nothing.

895
01:12:43,684 --> 01:12:46,414
No money, no friends, nothing.

896
01:12:46,487 --> 01:12:48,649
If I stay, I got you.

897
01:12:48,723 --> 01:12:53,252
Anyone finds out I'm alive...
you're dead, so...

898
01:12:55,397 --> 01:12:57,423
I got-- I got you, Tommy.

899
01:12:59,936 --> 01:13:03,338
What's the matter?
You got nothing to crack wise about?

900
01:13:03,407 --> 01:13:05,841
Bernie ain't
so funny anymore?

901
01:13:09,114 --> 01:13:12,049
I guess I made kind of
a fool of myself out there...

902
01:13:14,254 --> 01:13:16,745
bawling away like a twist.

903
01:13:16,823 --> 01:13:19,258
I guess--

904
01:13:19,326 --> 01:13:21,260
I guess I turned yellow.

905
01:13:21,328 --> 01:13:25,026
