908
01:13:35,312 --> 01:13:40,148
and I can't help remembering
that you put the finger on me,

909
01:13:40,218 --> 01:13:43,312
and you took me out there to whack me.

910
01:13:43,388 --> 01:13:47,018
I know... you didn't.
I know.

911
01:13:47,092 --> 01:13:50,893
