923
01:14:55,340 --> 01:14:57,571
Oof.

924
01:15:01,414 --> 01:15:04,248
Uuh!

925
01:15:04,318 --> 01:15:06,411
You make me laugh, Tommy.

926
01:15:06,487 --> 01:15:10,049
You're gonna catch cold.
Then you're no good to me.

927
01:15:10,125 --> 01:15:13,061
